dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipal boundaries for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NWashburn_Municipalities_2018.gdbN. [The municipal boundary feature class is a polygon file of all Towns, Villages and Cities within Washburn County. The data was developed using a variety of sources including, but not limited to, PLSS breakdown, surveyor records, road records, and deed descriptions.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
